For ClimOO purposes, we intend astronomical objects, astronomical bodies and related parts as to be interpretable as complex system (and system environments). We envision having discussions with subject matter experts about whether some of astronomical entities may be interpreted as systems (and system environments) that are not complex."""@en ,
