###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001795
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001795> rdfs:subClassOf _:genid83 ;
                                               rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
For ClimOO Ontology purposes, we restricted this class to processes having as occurrent part only ecosystem interactions and interaction among ecosystems and related environments. We excluded interactions happening into ecosystem environment, as for the related superclass.
See also “environmental system process” class.
http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500000"""@en .

_:genid83 rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
           owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000117> ;
           owl:someValuesFrom [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                owl:unionOf ( :ClimOO_0000038
                                              :ClimOO_0000046
                                            )
                              ] .

