<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_00002005> rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
Axioms detailing the additional elements that compose air may be reintroduced from EnvO, as needed."""@en .


<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000952> <http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/definition> """ClimOO developer comment:
It seems that there is some inconsistence with the use of the term “environment” and “ecosystem” in the definition of this class. The superclass refers to ecosystems. Here the focus is on natural environment. Currently, we maintain this class as it is. We, however, suggest revisions."""@en .


<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000009> rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
We constructed an initial alignment between IAO a CCO representation of ICE and measurements. It is tentative. We envision discussions with subject matter experts to revise and implement the work done so far."""@en ;
                                             rdfs:seeAlso """http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000583 
http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000039
http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000221""" .


<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000027> rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
We constructed an initial alignment between IAO a CCO representation of ICE and measurements. It is tentative. We envision discussions with subject matter experts to revise and implement the work done so far."""@en .


<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000043> rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
Additional subclasses can be included to represent other supply chains and activities, pertaining to other systems, as needed. Similarly, some environmental processes can be classify as subclasses here or related to some activities, as neeed."""@en ,
                                                    """ClimOO developer comment:
ClimOO Ontology imports classes addressing supply chains and activities from SuMSO. Currently, the focus of these classes is restricted to supply chains and activities pertaining to the system of interest. They do not refer to supply chains and related activities pertaining to the related system environment. Implementations can be performed if needed."""@en .


<https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000041> rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
Some other ClimOO Ontology’s qualities and realizable entities can be further included as subclasses here, if needed."""@en .


